---
title: Peking Tofu & Mushroom Stir-Fry with Garlic–Ginger Rice & Crushed Peanuts
description: Behind every great stir-fry, there's got to be a great sauce! This one has Peking-style marinade, lime zest and soy sauce – it's a knockout. Toss it through tofu and a medley of veggies for a fast and easy weeknight winner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/peking-tofu-mushroom-stir-fry-76057766.jpg
